    <!-- Entrepreneurial Journey Section -->
    <section id="journey">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>My Entrepreneurial Journey</h2>
                <p>From identifying healthcare disparities to developing a telemedicine solution</p>
            </div>
            <div class="journey-content">
                <div>
                    <h3>Overview</h3>
                    <p>My journey began when I witnessed firsthand the healthcare disparities in rural and low-income communities. Despite technological advances, many people still lack access to basic healthcare services due to geographical, financial, and systemic barriers.</p>
                    <p>I spent months researching, interviewing patients and healthcare providers, and analyzing healthcare access data to understand the core challenges and validate the need for an accessible telemedicine solution.</p>
                    
                    <div class="stats">
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">46%</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Of rural residents lack specialist access</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">28%</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Longer travel time to healthcare facilities</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">65%</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Would use telehealth if available</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">3.6x</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Higher chronic disease rates in underserved areas</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="problem-box">
                    <h3>The Healthcare Access Problem</h3>
                    <p>Millions face barriers to healthcare access due to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Geographic isolation from medical facilities</li>
                        <li>Transportation challenges and costs</li>
                        <li>Shortage of healthcare providers in rural areas</li>
                        <li>Financial constraints and lack of insurance</li>
                        <li>Long wait times for appointments</li>
                        <li>Language and cultural barriers</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Validated Data:</strong> Research shows that rural residents are 40% less likely to have access to mental health services and 30% more likely to have chronic conditions that go unmanaged due to access barriers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section id="solution">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>The HealthConnect Solution</h2>
                <p>A comprehensive telemedicine platform designed for accessibility and equity</p>
            </div>
            <div class="solution-features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3><span class="feature-icon">üíª</span> Easy-to-Use Platform</h3>
                    <p>An intuitive interface that works on low-bandwidth connections, designed for users with varying levels of tech proficiency.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3><span class="feature-icon">üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è</span> Diverse Specialist Network</h3>
                    <p>Access to healthcare providers across multiple specialties, with language translation services and cultural competency training.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3><span class="feature-icon">üì±</span> Mobile-First Design</h3>
                    <p>Fully responsive design with SMS-based options for areas with limited smartphone or internet access.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Implementation Plan</h3>
                <p>The solution will be rolled out in three strategic phases:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Phase 1:</strong> Core telemedicine platform with video consultations, secure messaging, and basic health records</li>
                    <li><strong>Phase 2:</strong> Integration with community health workers, diagnostic tools, and prescription services</li>
                    <li><strong>Phase 3:</strong> AI-powered triage, chronic disease management programs, and partnerships with local clinics</li>
                </ol>
                
                <h3>Unique Value Propositions</h3>
                <ul class="usp-list">
                    <li>Sliding scale payment options based on income verification</li>
                    <li>Offline functionality for areas with intermittent connectivity</li>
                    <li>Multilingual support and culturally competent care</li>
                    <li>Integration with existing community health resources</li>
                    <li>Focus on preventive care and health education</li>
                    <li>Designed with input from underserved communities</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

